  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " id="shortdesc" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:29" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/common/reuse-w-lwdita/reuse-fn.dita">A footnote is ancillary information that typically is rendered in the
    footer of a page or at the end of an online article. Such content is usually inappropriate for
    inline inclusion.</shortdesc>
